parameters: \nw[Weapon Shop]Oh, we have some good stuff here.
\nw[Armor Shop]Thank you for the Armor Shop.

\nw[Nonna]Once your level goes up, you'll be able to equip
new gear. Equipment is important, so it's better
to update it regularly.

\nw[Nonna]Make sure to prepare properly. Not only your
equipment, but also make sure to have plenty of
healing potions.
\nw[Taro]I know. It's such a huge monster after all.

\nw[Nonna]Battles are decided 80% in the preparation stage.
Since it's a matter of life and death, be careful.
\nw[Taro]Oh, since I became the leader, leave it to me.
